translate English day7_60d84163:



    nvl clear
    "\n I find myself unable to sleep. After finally drifting into unconsciousness, a feather falls from my pillow. {w}The soft sound startles me awake."


translate English day7_2ff6edd2:


    "As my anxiety increases, the sound of wings flapping grows stronger, blurring the already fuzzy line between reality and dreams."


translate English day7_c719be64:


    "In the end, unable to win out against my fear, I lay there in my dark futon as my mind replays the events of the past week."


translate English day7_abbeb4be:


    et "The various people I've met and the incidents and accidents that have occurred thus far..."


translate English day7_6ac8199c:



    nvl clear
    "\n As the pitch-black sky gradually takes on an azure hue, the glow from the rising sun announces the start of a new day. {w}The dawn of my final day in the Cleanup Department has arrived far too quickly."


translate English day7_5af1f3cc:


    "Can I really move on to another department without getting proper closure with Maya? Doesn't help that I still don't feel like any of this is real."


translate English day7_11b8727e:


    "Is it really okay for me to accept this opportunity that's basically fallen into my lap? Why exactly do they want me? Is it because of my power?"


translate English day7_14847d95:


    et "Why do I have this much power to begin with? {w}Does such power even truly exist to begin with? I find myself growing progressively more awake with each passing thought."


translate English day7_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_37b89a44:


    "\n Unable to go back to sleep no matter what I try, I decide to head out into the chilly air. {w}Despite having left my room much earlier than usual, I can't bring myself to head toward the Cleanup Department."


translate English day7_6b183245:


    "With the sun just barely over the horizon, the temple is still empty. {w}I walk in the direction of an internally predetermined location."


translate English day7_1965fc4e:


    "As my anxiety increases, the sound of wings flapping grows stronger, blurring the already fuzzy line between reality and dreams."


translate English day7_e17538dc:


    et "As I lose myself in thought, I'm able to easily forget about everything that happened yesterday. I wish I could do the same about the past week. {w}Is this my decision, or something forced on me?"


translate English day7_84af5fee:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I'm asking what you think you can do on the Disposal Team here in the Underworld.\""


translate English day7_66bde872:


    "I never wanted to do any of this. If I had known then what I do now, I would've never come here."


translate English day7_c7c4f289:


    "I'm afraid. I have been ever since realizing how close I am to my own death."


translate English day7_023e94e7:


    "How many chances do I have left? Ever since arriving here, I've constantly had to face realities I've never encountered before. {w}And even with those experiences, I'm not ready for more."


translate English day7_3b9e5188:


    "\"What I mean is, I'm looking forward to seeing what you're capable of.\""


translate English day7_e2ffe6bc:


    et "I'm ready to give it everything I've got--at the risk of my very life."


translate English day7_71cd5105:



    nvl clear
    "\n I've worked more than anyone for this future, and now I feel strangled by lofty expectations."


translate English day7_e759d7f9:


    "I can't afford to worry about tomorrow. Feeling trapped in the past, nothing around me feels real right now."


translate English day7_0a2d072c:


    "Even preparing myself to stand by her side feels like someone else's problem."


translate English day7_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_b046ce86:


    nar "A space immersed in the darkness of night cannot know the brilliance of the light of day. {w}It exists in a cocoon."


translate English day7_15113be1:


    nar "There she is. The jet-black night sky seems to blend into her hair, spread out in a halo around her head. Her vividly colored eyes are wide open."


translate English day7_87168af6:


    nar "She looks surprised at first, but then immediately comes to a halt. {w}The light that brushes past her seems brighter than anything else in the world around us."


translate English day7_1f4bf9e9:


    ar "What brought you here?"


translate English day7_89c4bf19:


    nar "She nods, as if hearing an anticipated answer."


translate English day7_5a0507da:


    ar "I was thinking of you, from the depths of my soul. {w}I know it's cold, and yet for some reason, I can't seem to calm down. It's kind of embarrassing."


translate English day7_52461d93:


    ar "I see an impure light reflected in your eyes, Brother."


translate English day7_863d67c6:


    nar "She smiles at me sadly, my thoughts an open book to her. {w}She sees every lie I utter for what they are."


translate English day7_42699c62:


    nar "I wish I could come up with some kind of excuse, but I just can't. {w}My heart aches for the hurt I've caused her."


translate English day7_9da852b6:


    pl "I'm sorry..."


translate English day7_1e526581:


    ar "Do you feel bad for me, Brother?"


translate English day7_62be205a:


    pl "What do you mean?"


translate English day7_6ff0b74b:


    ar "I assume you feel responsible for the things he said to me."


translate English day7_a322955c:


    ar "You want to marry me and become my husband, correct?"


translate English day7_d32e0c33:


    pl "You're absurdly perceptive. Does this kind of thing happen often?"


translate English day7_172294af:


    ar "No. {w}You're the first in my entire life."


translate English day7_e2583ad3:


    pl "Don't say that... It puts way too much pressure on me."


translate English day7_604d0fee:


    ar "You're so kind. {w}I'm glad that you're the one God blessed me with."


translate English day7_15ee0602:


    nar "This is the second time she's said so, though my feelings on the matter haven't changed."


translate English day7_cb656993:


    pl "Technically, your uncle brought us together, right? God had nothing to do with it."


translate English day7_4a9ac7ca:


    pl "Please stop... {w}It doesn't make me happy to be forced into being with you. And I mean that."


translate English day7_f7df13cb:


    pl "I'm glad I was able to get through to you. {w}Both you and your brother did a great job pretending to act grown up while flattering that strange man."


translate English day7_c641b530:


    pl "Though you didn't have to do that. I would've kept my mouth shut regardless."


translate English day7_15b639e4:


    ar "You see me as nothing more than a puppet controlled by the Alternata family."


translate English day7_254159e4:


    ar "Everything I do is nothing more than an attempt at talking you into going through with this, hrm?"


translate English day7_876f5805:


    ar "Mm, I understand. I can see why you think that way."


translate English day7_ade16ae4:


    ar "But you're wrong. {w}I chose you, as did the Magic Department."


translate English day7_1326f57c:


    ar "I am not someone who is so fragile that I would bend to another's will so easily. {w}Nor is my family so vile that we would ignore the wishes of our fellow brethren."


translate English day7_78ce0ef2:


    ar "Right now, you are more important than you realize, Brother... {w}And I understand that we have yet to earn your trust. {w}I feel guilty, especially for the burden we've placed on you."


translate English day7_d6c31c9e:


    ar "Don't feel like you have to join the Magic Department if you don't want to."


translate English day7_b205d863:


    pl "What...?"


translate English day7_69c84ff7:


    ar "Let me be completely honest. You are more than welcome to stay in the Cleanup Department if that is what you wish."


translate English day7_c836ebe4:


    ar "Granted, even if you leave the temple, we promise that your stay in the capital shall not be in vain."


translate English day7_1d743ebb:


    pl "You're really not making this easy, you know? {w}There's no way I could make a decision that might turn that many people against me."


translate English day7_fabe64d8:


    pl "Don't say anything you'll end up regretting later, Sister."


translate English day7_501331ac:


    ar "I chose you. {w}The Magic Department was ready to accept you into our family, as one of us."


translate English day7_ede7dbc7:


    ar "Yet you turned down our selfish request. That's all."


translate English day7_6b6a13e6:


    ar "So don't worry. I promise to take care of you until the very end."


translate English day7_249e324f:


    pl "Why me? There's other people way more deserving."


translate English day7_c0f0ee5e:


    ar "There is no other. {w}As you once so rightfully stated, I have my own fears."


translate English day7_1d3e9e95:


    ar "We live our entire lives among strangers. That's all the Alternata women are born to do."


translate English day7_d1c41007:


    ar "You should have referred to me as a soulless puppet. {w}I acted like everything was fine, yet my uncle was always aware of the unhappiness I felt."


translate English day7_a749aa9c:


    ar "And yet my heart has belonged to you, Brother, from the moment I first met you."


translate English day7_674e3582:


    ar "Making your will, and your desires, absolute to me. How can I explain this reaction other than that you're a gift from God?"


translate English day7_eb1e660c:


    pl "..."


translate English day7_a1b9132d:


    ar "I can see you still don't believe me. {w}I apologize. I seem to have a harder time expressing my emotions than others."


translate English day7_efca5250:


    ar "Yet I still feel you are mistaken about us, Brother. About the Magic Department, that is."


translate English day7_14289c4a:


    pl "You're acting far too seriously for anything to make sense. Also, we've gone completely off-topic."


translate English day7_52c30fad:


    pl "With that said, I can tell that you're not a liar."


translate English day7_0e96439e:


    pl "I keep my promises..."


translate English day7_2a570292:


    nar "I extend a hand toward her without looking in her direction, though I can feel her gaze fixed on me, even as she takes my hand in hers."


translate English day7_36285a75:


    ar "Of course. {w}I eagerly await whatever decision you come to."


translate English day7_bdefa13c:


    pl "There's no hidden meaning to what I said."


translate English day7_d8b094f4:


    pl "It's impossible for me to take this seriously."


translate English day7_f7b7f5ca:


    pl "I'm not at all ready to accept anything the bishop said... About my abilities or about this marriage business."


translate English day7_9afa7723:


    ar "Do you hate me, Brother?"


translate English day7_e4501d1b:


    ar "You clearly despise me for the unimaginable burden that's been placed on you thanks to me..."


translate English day7_6ddf7046:


    pl "That's right. {w}I do despise you."


translate English day7_a786f1ff:


    pl "I didn't come all the way to the capital just be used by you. {w}I don't understand this ability you all keep saying I have."


translate English day7_761cd4ff:


    pl "What is it that you all want with me? {w}The only thing you and your brother come off as are hypocrites trying to take advantage of me."


translate English day7_61125bda:


    ar "Can I say something that might sound strange...?"


translate English day7_863022bd:


    ar "I am relieved. Utterly so."


translate English day7_67f6dccd:


    ar "I am relieved that you're so honest with me about how you feel, that you look down on me as nothing more than a mere human, fills me with indescribable relief."


translate English day7_6867cabf:


    nar "She smiles at me gently."


translate English day7_1e43fcfe:


    nar "I can try to deny her smile all I want, so beautiful that it eclipses how rotten her soul has become, and yet I cannot deny the truth behind her words."


translate English day7_ca9cf208:


    ar "First of all, I owe you an apology. {w}I'm sorry that my carelessness might have caused you anxiety."


translate English day7_c947e2e9:


    ar "Though it's true this all started from me initially offering you my help, {w}I almost cannot bring myself to face you knowing that I should have made a move sooner."


translate English day7_9266d8ac:


    pl "Making excuses now, are you?"


translate English day7_bc92cf89:


    ar "Unfortunately, I am not that skilled. {w}I'm bad enough at talking about my own true emotions, let alone embellishing them."


translate English day7_9d4750f9:


    ar "Which is why I admire you so much. {w}You always know just what to say in order to lighten the mood of those around you. It's a talent I simply do not possess."


translate English day7_0b809eda:


    pl "I told you to stop mocking me! That's just a roundabout way of calling yourself a coward, isn't it? {w}Without the confidence to take responsibility for anything, all you end up doing is running away whenever the going gets tough."


translate English day7_1d996d1c:


    pl "What exactly do you want me to say? {w}Is this fun for you? {w}Talking with you is like yelling at a wall!"


translate English day7_826881ae:


    nar "The words coming from my mouth gradually begin making less and less sense. {w}Does she understand how I feel? She merely stands there, watching me silently."


translate English day7_4382e6eb:


    nar "I'm unable to see her face in my slumped over position. {w}I try to conjure up an image of her face from my disordered thoughts."


translate English day7_95a29d20:


    nar "Is she reveling in my suffering? Or does she look panicked, caught completely off guard?"


translate English day7_8d3278bc:


    nar "It's just the image I have of her in my mind, and yet... I can't see anything."


translate English day7_8b9c108d:


    nar "She's so weird. {w}I'm the one hurling hurtful insults and yet I'm also the only one who feels ashamed. {w}At the end of the day, I have to face down my own problems."


translate English day7_9f4f1202:


    nar "When I say things like this, I'm doing nothing but using her as a punching bag for my own frustrations."


translate English day7_981495ea:


    nar "I suddenly feel the touch of her cold hand on mine. {w}Surprised, I reflexively pull my hand back."


translate English day7_22701298:


    nar "I meet her gaze with my own. {w}She clasps her hands against her chest, as if adopting my own suffering into herself."


translate English day7_b9257b7c:


    ar "You're shaking..."


translate English day7_6ebd2f43:


    ar "It pains me to be unable to understand how you feel."


translate English day7_d35e50ab:


    pl "That's right. You'll never be able to understand."


translate English day7_b6a9ec42:


    ar "But, Brother. There's one thing I want you to know."


translate English day7_ef15520a:


    ar "The Magic Department has no intention of suppressing you in any way."


translate English day7_03ca27ab:


    ar "And neither do I."


translate English day7_49b5aefa:


    ar "I want to know what your true desire is, Brother."


translate English day7_a3c90c95:


    pl "What good will that do?"


translate English day7_78c27ca1:


    ar "I can guarantee that whatever you desire will come to be..."


translate English day7_f8cd14df:


    ar "If it's wanting to remain in the Cleanup Department or leaving the temple entirely to start a new life in the capital... {w}Those of us in the Magic Department have vowed to obey whatever desire you have."


translate English day7_25c8d1de:


    pl "So you're basically abandoning me because I won't do what you want?"


translate English day7_f64466f1:


    ar "..."


translate English day7_50203503:


    nar "Knowing full well that this is all an act of sorts, my reply is meant as a slap in the face."


translate English day7_eb68f0da:


    nar "But she neither confirms nor denies my accusation. {w}Instead, she looks back at me, her gaze unwaveringly steady, before reaching out to me once more."


translate English day7_c396fb18:


    nar "Though no matter how much she might deny it, there's no escape. {w}She already knows every mistake I've made thus far."


translate English day7_8a63f5de:


    nar "That's the power she holds over me. The power to bring those around her to their knees."


translate English day7_4be17b5e:


    nar "Throwing off my bewilderment, I take her hand in mine."


translate English day7_100cea5e:


    nar "Her ice-cold grip is, as always, resolutely firm. I never stood a chance against her."


translate English day7_0e96439e_1:


    pl "I keep my promises..."


translate English day7_36285a75_1:


    ar "Of course. {w}I eagerly await whatever decision you come to."


translate English day7_0bce9e94:


    "\n With the tension lifted, my sleep-deprived brain is suddenly assaulted by a wave of drowsiness. {w}Even after stumbling back to my room, though, I find it impossible to fall asleep."


translate English day7_47a2637f:


    "The room contorts around me from a severely insufficient amount of sleep. There's an incessant ringing in my ears. {w}The sound seems to grow louder by the day."


translate English day7_c74b6a60:


    "The noise seems to bring the shadows in my room into sharp relief, spinning and spiraling around me. {w}There's a rotten stench in the air, though I can't tell if it's real or imagined."


translate English day7_c6434e2f:


    "I shake my head violently to dispel the scent. It's clear my lack of sleep is to blame."


translate English day7_b24d8cdd:


    "It's my last day with the Cleanup Department. {w}It still doesn't feel real."


translate English day7_77d97558:


    et "I hold out my hand, looking down at my outstretched arm. {w}The black scar that mars my skin makes it resemble desolate ground split by a dried-up river."


translate English day7_37f49fe3:


    nar "By the time I've dragged my leaden body to the Cleanup Department, the morning meeting has long since been over."


translate English day7_80542cab:


    nar "Having been late already once before, I feel like my normally high standards are in complete disarray."


translate English day7_523f2efb:


    cr "Well, well!"


translate English day7_6b2de0a2:


    nar "The last person I expected to see is leaning against the wall just outside the entrance. {w}As if alerted to my presence by my footsteps, she turns, her eyes as wide as saucers."


translate English day7_3cf8eb82:


    cr "He's finally here!"


translate English day7_6173d50d:


    nar "Before I even have time to register my own surprise, she's dived into the doorway, and I can hear her faint voice announcing my presence."


translate English day7_3d74ae2b:


    nar "Who could possibly still be here? My anxious mind is all too happy to provide me with some possibilities, one image after another."


translate English day7_27897a90:


    nar "I ended up worrying for nothing, however. {w}It was only her."


translate English day7_4e6e4276:


    my "Morning, [na2]. You're late."


translate English day7_49b577b1:


    pl "I know, I know... Ah, morning, Maya."


translate English day7_e838d78c:


    pl "What are you two doing together? It's pretty late for you to still be here..."


translate English day7_2a51fcbe:


    cr "Oh, gosh! {w}Why can't I be here? I am, after all, one of Saint Sheol's prominent benefactors."


translate English day7_a82a4952:


    cr "There's no problem with letting the aura of the Cleanup Department seep into my skin and lungs, right?"


translate English day7_9ea1e634:


    pl "I'm not sure I can promise that, considering you'll probably have to toss all those expensive clothes of yours after."


translate English day7_0f41c8ea:


    pl "You'll make a great number of people sad, including myself, if the stench from the Disposal Team gets on your clothes, Miss Clione. {w}What I'm trying to say is..."


translate English day7_cc6c7450:


    cr "Right! {w}Yes, I will marry you!!!"


translate English day7_95d659e6:


    nar "Marriage... The weight of this single word, uttered so casually, causes my heart to skip a beat."


translate English day7_17b265d8:


    cr "You don't have to say anything. {w}We'll hold the ceremony in a month's time, on the day of the harvest!"


translate English day7_76fab72b:


    cr "Sadly, the timing means I won't be a bride of the Flower Moon, but I know I can make you happy!"


translate English day7_e12ef755:


    cr "We'll have a festive celebration worthy of inviting all of our friends and family. {w}Though it's a shame that you'll be in charge of providing the officiant..."


translate English day7_0d4340ca:


    nar "As her uninterrupted monologue flows seemingly endlessly from her mouth, {w}I feel a chill race up my spine, as if all the blood in my head is flowing elsewhere."


translate English day7_c7bb5eb1:


    nar "I try to say something, but nothing comes out above a hoarse croak. {w}My throat's gotten dry at some point."


translate English day7_6bf2dd47:


    my "You came out here today to celebrate with us, right, Claire?"


translate English day7_2ee053ae:


    cr "That's right! {w}Gosh! I'm sorry for being so rude. All I seem to talk about lately is this wedding..."


translate English day7_d969ba9b:


    pl "Celebrate? What are we celebrating?"


translate English day7_fcb5416e:


    nar "Maya is able to interrupt the young girl's incessant chattering. {w}This is my chance to change the topic."


translate English day7_4dbc5387:


    cr "Celebrating the fact that, as of today, Maya has become a full-fledged priest here at Saint Sheol!"


translate English day7_7301b13b:


    cr "Is it not a glorious day when my beloved sister can finally become an official member of the temple after her long and arduous journey to get there? {w}I feel obliged to congratulate her!"


translate English day7_bf774270:


    nar "Luckily, it seems like my distraction tactic was effective. {w}I discretely take a deep breath as I try to regain my composure."


translate English day7_c86e971f:


    pl "She's not really your sister, you know. {w}Try not to cause her any problems."


translate English day7_a8eb8f83:


    cr "You're the only one causing any problems! {w}Making Maya wait all this time for YOU to finally show up!"


translate English day7_5b42f047:


    pl "What?"


translate English day7_39cdee8d:


    my "I, uh... {w}I wanted to spend your last day here with you, but I started to worry since you were so late..."


translate English day7_efc23ca2:


    nar "My face which had stiffened awkwardly since I arrived was now on fire. {w}I wouldn't be surprised if my discomfort was evident to everyone in the room."


translate English day7_eefc9c78:


    nar "My heart, which had begun to beat frantically, suddenly freezes when I feel cold fingers on the back of my neck."


translate English day7_eb114b82:


    pl "Eep!!!"


translate English day7_10e15d15:


    sc "What a sordid scream."


translate English day7_0cc08f66:


    pl "Wh-What do you think you're doing, coming out of nowhere like that, Securett?! {w}Do the folks here in the temple not understand the simple act of saying hello?"


translate English day7_770bcd30:


    sc "Yes, yes. You're one to talk, considering how late you were."


translate English day7_fa755c43:


    pl "What's going on? What are you doing here in the temple at this time of day?"


translate English day7_6f39cae4:


    pl "Don't tell me you were looking for me?"


translate English day7_8418a765:


    sc "You've got some high hopes there. I'm here on business. {w}Also, I figured you wouldn't be in any hurry to get here knowing what's going on."


translate English day7_b5623b2a:


    sc "Besides, it'd be a huge waste of time to deliberately hunt down the problem child who always seems to be underfoot, right?"


translate English day7_e2669b21:


    pl "You're a big important man, huh?"


translate English day7_f69e3fdd:


    sc "Lord above, you've gotten on my last nerve."


translate English day7_3b2750e0:


    sc "That includes you, Maya. {w}You've managed to mess things up royally throughout your probation period. {w}How do you plan on taking responsibility for the work that's piled up thanks to you?"


translate English day7_47ed2cc0:


    pl "Oh, right. Today's her last day, huh? {w}Since we've already made an epic mess of our job, why stop now? There's always room for more extravagant mistakes."


translate English day7_ccd365f6:


    my "Extravagant...?"


translate English day7_705445cc:


    cr "Extravagant!"


translate English day7_93316c25:


    sc "You're all lost causes."


translate English day7_6deba8d9:


    pl "That's right, we've all lost our damn minds! {w}From being here for too long."


translate English day7_d8e19b30:


    nar "The two girls' eyes sparkle with anticipation, as if empowered by my sudden declaration."


translate English day7_4d127739:


    nar "There's clearly something on Securett's mind as he glances over at them, though he almost immediately heaves one of his patented sighs of annoyance."


translate English day7_78fe0177:


    sc "Don't get any ideas."


translate English day7_bcc10742:


    sc "I was hoping the last few days would've taught you the importance of our job here, at least a little... {w}The Cleanup Department has suffered enough thanks to your self-centered actions."


translate English day7_81266dab:


    sc "Don't think you can let your responsibilities slide just because it's your last day, Maya."


translate English day7_d2c15d61:


    nar "The mood in the room has definitely soured. {w}With everyone silently scowling, Securett once again opens his mouth to speak."


translate English day7_b2342caf:


    sc "However..."


translate English day7_77a8b567:


    sc "You wouldn't be skipping out on work if you were on escort duty for Miss Myosotis."


translate English day7_961ab525:


    sc "I can try to get the bishop's approval for the afternoon to buy some time."


translate English day7_c859367b:


    nar "A fire is relighted in our eyes once again upon hearing that. {w}He's always doing frustrating things like this, leaving what he should have said first for his final thoughts."


translate English day7_8a962d96:


    nar "While I feel his actions are inexcusable, I'm also grateful at the same time."


translate English day7_f42dda44:


    nar "As if embarrassed at being showered in gazes of gratitude from all directions,"


translate English day7_f8f39d5d:


    nar "Securett immediately leaves the room without looking at any of us."


translate English day7_b84f10e2:


    cr "That was a surprise. {w}I always thought of him as a standoffish and rather cold guy, but he's become quite a softie, huh?"


translate English day7_d6ab6307:


    cr "Did something happen recently?"


translate English day7_7085c170:


    pl "I guess you're the type to think people only change if there's a reason to."


translate English day7_c2244f80:


    cr "At the very least, that's been my personal experience."


translate English day7_56af8291:


    pl "It's definitely true that most people won't act or change without a trigger."


translate English day7_cd2309b1:


    cr "Feelings that didn't exist previously can be born from specific situations, right?"


translate English day7_b4355be9:


    pl "Looks like you have the answer you want."


translate English day7_9a78fd25:


    cr "Looks that way."


translate English day7_a573988b:


    pl "Personally, I think we just got lucky."


translate English day7_9bdd17e5:


    cr "That's not helpful in the slightest..."


translate English day7_d85e2a94:


    pl "Well, knowing is half the battle!"


translate English day7_869d78bd:


    cr "Don't try changing the subject with weird compliments!"


translate English day7_33a82e19:


    pl "I'm being serious! Well... {w}I have a feeling we all change when the right time comes."


translate English day7_f14fbf92:


    my "Maybe..."


translate English day7_c44d8c19:


    nar "Maya suddenly pipes up after having stood there in silence, watching us."


translate English day7_26e78dd7:


    nar "She seemed to be pondering the situation quietly to herself instead of joining in."


translate English day7_572a5427:


    my "Maybe some people never change, even with the existence of a significant event."


translate English day7_e5d6b859:


    cr "You mean they can't accept the act of change itself?"


translate English day7_9dcbcf6c:


    my "No, that they refuse to grow."


translate English day7_9d989729:


    pl "What do you think about people like that, Maya?"


translate English day7_fefd0eb0:


    my "Me? {w} Hrm... Good question."


translate English day7_8634cf72:


    my "I think life is pretty tough if you have no purpose."


translate English day7_c2673cfd:


    my "It makes it hard to understand yourself, let alone the people around you."


translate English day7_c76b7925:


    nar "A murky view flows past the rattling windows. I never imagined I'd be back down this road again."


translate English day7_f3355dc1:


    nar "Though the train is far less crowded departing from the temple to the capital compared to coming from the opposite direction."


translate English day7_5ca31cf0:


    nar "Also, that fragile young girl with the light pink hair is sitting next to me this time."


translate English day7_8956872a:


    nar "I feel kind of sad being outside the temple without a bag or cart in either hand. {w}I'm sure they feel the same way."


translate English day7_3232de9a:


    nar "Before we'd left, Securett had explained to us the dangers of wandering the capital in our own clothes. {w}Though I'd already been well aware."


translate English day7_7c8f03b2:


    nar "Maya seemed especially depressed upon hearing it. {w}I was kind of let down as well, since I have a feeling she must be incredibly adorable decked out in her own clothing."


translate English day7_22c01bd8:


    nar "The town before us is packed full of stores. {w}Seeing all manner of people around us dressed in colorful clothing and feeling the air questionably ripe following a recent rainstorm,"


translate English day7_71cd4196:


    nar "I'm filled with the certainty that this is going to be a great day."


translate English day7_42a00435:


    nar "It has to be, I think to myself, almost like a vow of sorts."


translate English day7_b8a60220:


    pl "It's so nice out here! It would've been the perfect picnic weather if it was a little sunnier."


translate English day7_dabfd3a0:


    cr "Though having all the lights on in the middle of a dark day is pretty festive, right?"


translate English day7_cf4bb3c9:


    pl "You've got a point."


translate English day7_931de85e:


    nar "Maya, who'd been walking behind us with her head down suddenly stops. {w}I follow the direction of her gaze to see a poster hanging on a wall."


translate English day7_1a812f40:


    nar "It shows a group of men, none of whom are priests, all dressed in pure black."


translate English day7_10db6857:


    nar "Their faces are covered in various colors and designs, though it's hard to make out due to the harsh backlighting."


translate English day7_f500e140:


    sc "Interested? {w}It's a performance by the city's orchestra."


translate English day7_57e2892f:


    cr "This city's got some poor taste, if you ask me..."


translate English day7_d78f3538:


    my "Really? I think it looks pretty cool..."


translate English day7_4eae6809:


    cr "I love that you have a fascination for music, dear sister Maya! {w}Why don't we check it out?"


translate English day7_854d9c33:


    pl "Didn't you just say you thought it was in bad taste...?"


translate English day7_9c087d27:


    cr "They say that guys who are overly critical of everything another person says have a higher chance, statistically speaking, of having type O blood."


translate English day7_e241b0c6:


    pl "I'm sorry to disappoint, but I'm actually type A."


translate English day7_45c3dc1f:


    cr "Unfortunately for you, I already knew that."


translate English day7_00785f19:


    sc "Do you two need a room or something?"


translate English day7_9d5b011c:


    nar "A man, bathed in systematically flashing lights, stands in the front of the room, pouring his heart and soul into a sad love song."


translate English day7_d5580d61:


    nar "The room is dark. I'm leaning back in a chair. The gentle sound of instruments playing swirls around me."


translate English day7_d2395cb6:


    nar "The occasional boisterous melody or the sudden sound of drums temporarily rouses me from my drowsiness, forcing my eyelids to snap open."


translate English day7_e3adefb4:


    nar "The seats in front of us are empty except for a few other patrons. One couple in particular catches my attention. {w}It's a young man and woman, their bodies moving in the darkness."


translate English day7_e30d3ee1:


    nar "With their bodies mostly hidden by the backs of their chairs, they seem to be grinning at each other about something."


translate English day7_f6ae1cfa:


    nar "I can hear the titillating sound of their breathing clearly over the music."


translate English day7_f93014b3:


    nar "As I silently stare at the scene before me, I suddenly feel the urge to vomit well up inside me and crouch over, covering my mouth with my hand."


translate English day7_6c8ae36b:


    nar "The sound of the girl's exaggerated nasally voice grates on my ears, causing my stomach to heave."


translate English day7_641efe93:


    my "That was wonderful..."


translate English day7_a61763f4:


    sc "You like this kind of thing, huh?"


translate English day7_b684b4e3:


    my "Huh? I g-guess I'm pretty strange..."


translate English day7_61606526:


    sc "No. {w}I think it's great."


translate English day7_de08fbcf:


    sc "Thank you for providing me with such a marvelous experience."


translate English day7_532fb550:


    my "Mmm..."


translate English day7_2f5e6537:


    cr "You don't look so well, Lord [na]."


translate English day7_2f598ca8:


    my "You didn't enjoy it, [na2]?"


translate English day7_11329692:


    pl "N-No! That's not true..."


translate English day7_53fa96d9:


    pl "There was a couple sitting in front of us who were acting pretty impolite... {w}I can't believe they were doing something like *that* in public."


translate English day7_2ec10603:


    cr "Is that so? I don't remember seeing anyone behaving like that in the theater."


translate English day7_451cd209:


    pl "Probably better you didn't. You probably couldn't see them since you're so small. {w}Were you even able to see the performance at all?"


translate English day7_ec29687b:


    cr "What a rude thing to say to a lady!!! I saw the performance quite well, thank you! {w}In fact, I can still see it quite vividly in my mind's eye."


translate English day7_211121d5:


    cr "Once I get home, I'll be sure to write down my thoughts on some pretty stationery"


translate English day7_2e9fac60:


    cr "so I can send it to poor, sweet Lord [na], who wasn't able to share the same experience with us!"


translate English day7_0b5fd61a:


    my "I'm just glad that you enjoyed it, Claire. We should talk about it some other time."


translate English day7_c16b0593:


    cr "Yaaaaay! {w}Being able to share things with my dear, dear sister Maya makes me even happier!"


translate English day7_0af1eaa0:


    nar "Our next stop was at a woman's clothing store in town. {w}The light glittering off the abundance of heavy metals visible from the street attractions draws the attention of folks walking by."


translate English day7_c30f606c:


    nar "Clione, who is far from impervious to the inviting sight, tugs on Maya's arm. {w}The two girls tentatively step inside the store."


translate English day7_255ef3ef:


    cr "Do you want to come inside with us, Securett?"


translate English day7_9790ecbb:


    sc "Wh-What kind of stupid question is that?! {w}I'm a man!!!"


translate English day7_c9eb67ed:


    pl "In that case, I'll happily take your spot."


translate English day7_1d0a6f22:


    cr "Make sure your heart is ready, for the women stepping out of the changing rooms are very beautiful indeed!"


translate English day7_8b569e81:


    pl "Yes, yes... {w}I'm sure Maya can pull off any look marvelously."


translate English day7_48d127c0:


    cr "And me, too?"


translate English day7_ff26833b:


    pl "Double yes."


translate English day7_6d171c8e:


    my "This broach would look good on you, Claire."


translate English day7_9a4d2b8b:


    pl "You, too, Maya! What if you each get one so you can match? {w}My treat!"


translate English day7_59bfb32c:


    sc "Don't forget that you're not getting paid for a little while longer."


translate English day7_0f8c38f9:


    cr "Girls don't like guys who always feel the need to rain on other's parades, Securett."


translate English day7_17658366:


    pl "She's right. {w}What do you think?"


translate English day7_acb7a7b2:


    sc "Well... I think it's nice. {w}It looks very cute on both of you."


translate English day7_763b2e5e:


    cr "Oh, gosh!"


translate English day7_ccab71b8:


    pl "That was very well said!"


translate English day7_7593d159:


    sc "Stop..."


translate English day7_ebf397b2:


    cr "Shall we both buy one, Miss Maya?"


translate English day7_3334fc23:


    my "..."


translate English day7_47142842:


    my "I don't need it..."


translate English day7_76e98eaa:


    nar "The midnight-blue sky contains streaks of purple. {w}Each splash of water from the fountain creates puddles on the ground, reflecting us upside down as we slowly begin the walk back."


translate English day7_aa73a959:


    nar "We ate some pretty tart ice cream for dessert. {w}Maya claps her hands, red from the cold, in the air in front of her."


translate English day7_2cb96885:


    my "It always feels like the world's shut down on polar summer nights like tonight..."


translate English day7_4669f0c3:


    pl "You prefer when the wind is so cold, it literally takes your breath away?"


translate English day7_cdfa578d:


    cr "There's something suspicious about the way you two are acting."


translate English day7_01ce55b2:


    pl "Yeah?"


translate English day7_0edd4697:


    cr "You've been acting rather buddy-buddy for a while now..."


translate English day7_1cd4c7ae:


    my "We have?"


translate English day7_3b9b68c3:


    nar "The two of us exchange glances. Maya immediately slouches over."


translate English day7_56d4707a:


    pl "What's the matter, munchkin? {w}Jealous?"


translate English day7_fd1b42fe:


    cr "Hmph! Someone's rather arrogant."


translate English day7_22991980:


    sc "Who are you talking about again?"


translate English day7_761ec30f:


    cr "[na] is the arrogant one!"


translate English day7_dc558a55:


    my "Hahaha..."


translate English day7_8c5ae16e:


    nar "The air is so crisp and clean that I can hear the tiny chirping of insects, seeming almost like a hallucination. {w}It definitely feels like fall."


translate English day7_6699ccef:


    nar "It's so cold in the capital. And with no sunrise or sunset, it feels so different from the summer sky I grew up with."


translate English day7_eedaeb33:


    nar "With each passing day spent in the capital, my memories of my hometown grow more distant, {w}to the point where I've grown to feel nothing when thinking about it."


translate English day7_1640bc3c:


    nar "We talked about circumstances changing a person, but in my opinion, {w}I believe the simple act of changing one's environment is often all it takes."


translate English day7_ec62f2c9:


    nar "And of course, the formation of memories that can be relived and looked back on."


translate English day7_02c0a44a:


    nar "Both myself and Securett quietly sit to the side, {w}watching from afar as the two girls stroll through the flower garden."


translate English day7_595b5485:


    sc "It wasn't quite as fun as you said it would be."


translate English day7_223be4e2:


    pl "I'd say your constantly negative attitude is to blame for that."


translate English day7_b8de2e7b:


    pl "From the way I saw it, it seems like you enjoyed it enough to lose yourself in the moment."


translate English day7_22ad8792:


    sc "Perhaps... {w}You know, I can tell she means a lot to you."


translate English day7_cab6f748:


    pl "Yeah?"


translate English day7_1df044b6:


    nar "I know exactly which \"she\" Securett's referring to."


translate English day7_0b34e609:


    pl "I do tend to get slightly flustered around her. {w}Though I don't understand why."


translate English day7_69bd837a:


    sc "I think I know why."


translate English day7_7631af35:


    pl "Do ya?"


translate English day7_969a7e9d:


    sc "You get too caught up in other things."


translate English day7_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_a837d565:


    "\n \"Whew! That was so much fun!\""


translate English day7_3d21102d:


    "Looking satisfied and yet slightly sad, the girl's innocent smile signals the end of our time together."


translate English day7_8620dabc:


    "The light sparkling in her eyes shines bright, even against the darkness. {w}This doll-like young girl seems right at home amongst the beautiful city streets within the solid city walls."


translate English day7_fc2d11f3:


    "I can almost see the line drawn between her and the three of us, unable to break free from the temple's shadow."


translate English day7_f61447dc:


    "\"I'm honored that you took a shining to your escort, Miss Myosotis.\""


translate English day7_e9c9fb96:


    "I perform a deep and overly exaggerated bow in an attempt at negating those uncomfortable feelings. {w}Clione laughs at my antics."


translate English day7_d778a9bb:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Who exactly are you pretending to be? ...Is what I'd like to say, but everyone's in such a good mood, I'll let it slide."


translate English day7_9c41115e:


    "Today was so much fun! Right, Miss Maya?\""


translate English day7_a63cd0cc:


    "\"It truly was.\""


translate English day7_cea3ccf9:


    "Maya's face seems to grow fuzzier with each listless word and forced smile. {w}Unlike me, she can't seem to muster the strength to push back the waves of depression."


translate English day7_37e772ec:


    "\"We should really get back.\""


translate English day7_90322223:


    "\"Sooner rather than later.\""


translate English day7_68eddf22:


    "Securett's calm voice, stating the facts as usual, sounds colder than usual."


translate English day7_9001f1c6:


    et "We're all well aware. I'm grateful for Maya's nod of affirmation, no matter how small it is."


translate English day7_a8a07173:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I'm so very grateful that you invited me to spend such an amazing day with you."


translate English day7_0db1be15:


    "I won't have as much free time moving forward, meaning I won't be able to visit the temple as often as before."


translate English day7_55be3a46:


    "So I wish to celebrate not only sister Maya's promotion but also the friendship between all of us. {w}The time we spent together was very fun!\""


translate English day7_91a06981:


    "Seeing Claire holding the hem of her skirt as she curtsies in our direction, signaling that we're free to go, {w}looks far more graceful than my poor attempt at the decorous gesture."


translate English day7_7a024cb5:


    et "Within that body lies the accumulation of the time we spent together. {w}Having only spent a week in the temple, a part of me wonders if I'll ever become a full-fledged priest."


translate English day7_c7fedd5e:



    nvl clear
    "\n A strong gust of wind leaves me no time to calm my chaotic mix of emotions. {w}A group of children hurrying past is who we have to thank for the sudden squall."


translate English day7_947cb329:


    "We all turn around at once, looking toward the source of the rude behavior. {w}The children's laughter combined with a loud splash is where everything starts to go wrong."


translate English day7_45a5fd12:


    "Summer in the rainy capital means puddles of muddy rain water. {w}And Maya finds herself pulling the short straw from the luck pile. {w}Though none of us can complain if that's the worst to befall us today."


translate English day7_d15f9af6:


    "\"No...\" {w}Gripping her now dirty skirt in one hand, she mutters that one word dispiritedly to herself under her breath."


translate English day7_521567eb:


    "The world momentarily falls silent, and her face crumples in grief. {w}She furrows her brow and opens her mouth wide as large tears begin dripping down her cheeks."


translate English day7_303b4562:


    et "Her eyes are filled with fear."


translate English day7_018b07a2:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"No! No, no, no! This can't be real!\" She shakes her head from side to side fearfully, repeating the same words over and over."


translate English day7_9b9b6ce6:


    "She seems so desperate to deny what just happened that it's impossible for me to calm her down in any way."


translate English day7_583134c8:


    "\"Sweet sister Maya...!\""


translate English day7_55fb01cc:


    "Claire approaches her with arms outstretched and Maya, crouched over as sobs wrack her body, crumples forward with not even the wherewithal to hug her back."


translate English day7_89987823:


    et "Unable to support the older girl's much heavier body weight, the two awkwardly sink to the ground. {w}They collapse where they stand."


translate English day7_ddabd272:



    nvl clear
    "\n Despair rips through my mind at seeing Maya, down on her knees on the muddy ground, wailing in grief."


translate English day7_9581986f:


    "My legs feel like two immovable blocks of stone. {w}I'd hoped that today would be nothing short of amazing."


translate English day7_06d6824e:


    "All I'd wanted was for Maya to experience a day of joy, one where she never stopped smiling. {w}And I'm sure she'd been hoping for the same thing."


translate English day7_d9287581:


    "I don't want Maya to be sad. {w}But the unreliable wall we'd built to protect her had easily come crashing down thanks to the ill-timed actions of some mischievous kids."


translate English day7_c194b65e:


    et "Why did this have to happen to us? {w}If this is nothing more than an extraordinarily bad stroke of luck, then surely this won't lead to Pestis, right?"


translate English day7_009dd9bb:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Not again.\""


translate English day7_06294e48:


    et "The words are spoken by a member of our group just as this previously pleasant day comes to a miserable end."


translate English day7_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_166d4d37:


    "\n On the way back to the temple after seeing Claire off, Securett looks at me and Maya as we watch the lights in town begin to go out, here and there."


translate English day7_41292656:


    "\"How about we take a little detour?\" {w}It's a suggestion he never would have uttered under normal circumstances."


translate English day7_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_8173910e:


    "\n He takes us to the last place I expected to find myself at--a secluded liquor store. {w}The wooden door creaks eerily, though there is no bell to signify our entrance."


translate English day7_06eb67cd:


    "One thing I've noticed about the capital is that most places don't want anything to do with the members of the Cleanup Department."


translate English day7_1e38d952:


    "The folks here seem repulsed by our very appearance, along with the unmistakable stench of death that clings to us."


translate English day7_d7e955ae:


    "This place alone, with its rotten walls smelling of alcohol, seems to welcome us in without prejudice, despite how late it is."


translate English day7_18844709:


    et "Rough-looking older men dressed in worn and dirty clothes dominate the available seats, scattered about the room. {w}The uneducated clientele thump each other noisily on the backs."


translate English day7_bf1d6b5f:



    nvl clear
    "\n They seem engrossed enough in their own revelry that they don't even seem to notice us. {w}The floor is covered in spilled beer and leftover porridge."


translate English day7_11e12828:


    et "An old man with a dirty beard seems unmindful of the chaos around him, mixing drinks silently behind the bar. {w}The atmosphere isn't bad, depending on how you look at it."


translate English day7_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_6e8c57f2:


    pl "I always pegged you as someone who prefers quieter pastimes."


translate English day7_bd2a4928:


    sc "An acquaintance dragged me here once."


translate English day7_be28b195:


    pl "You have friends other than us, Securett?"


translate English day7_7ea8f2ae:


    sc "And what if I do?"


translate English day7_8b24d91f:


    pl "If yes, then... I'm glad to hear that."


translate English day7_6aa360e2:


    nar "Two drinks and a meat pie quickly arrive at our table, and my worry over Maya proves unfounded as she unexpectedly--and without a hint of revulsion--accepts one of the glasses."


translate English day7_92deaea5:


    nar "The beer is lighter in color than what I'm used to back home."


translate English day7_b5e716f3:


    my "Looks like they cut it with water..."


translate English day7_f57b038e:


    pl "Huh? {w}This isn't your first time drinking, Maya?"


translate English day7_8db7b457:


    my "I... um... have a lot of brothers, so..."


translate English day7_e8d30bd5:


    sc "I find it far more implausible that someone your age has never had a drink before."


translate English day7_4b5ef4f5:


    pl "Why are you treating me like some foreign specimen just because I led a virtuous life?"


translate English day7_5810a7a2:


    sc "I'll settle us up, so if you want to order anything else, tell me now."


translate English day7_df916742:


    pl "Where are you going?"


translate English day7_38bb12cd:


    sc "Back to work."


translate English day7_246c6482:


    pl "Even though today's my last day?"


translate English day7_246eb5dc:


    sc "What does that have to do with anything?"


translate English day7_8f322915:


    my "Do you really have to go, Cue?"


translate English day7_54cd8c9a:


    sc "Sorry. At least one person will be in trouble if I stay much longer."


translate English day7_861c0248:


    sc "...Though that reminds me. {w}Congratulations on your promotions, both of you."


translate English day7_3334fc23_1:


    my "..."


translate English day7_512e946e:


    nar "With only the two of us remaining, Maya sits quietly, nursing her drink."


translate English day7_edfcc8e3:


    nar "The sight of her doing so gives me the courage to take a sip, and it tastes awful. {w}My empty stomach immediately revolts in pain."


translate English day7_2e012fe4:


    nar "She breaks the seemingly endless silence after taking a bite from a slice of the meat pie."


translate English day7_720543e4:


    my "This isn't very good..."


translate English day7_398017c8:


    pl "Yeah? Are you sure you don't like it?"


translate English day7_f6935cc3:


    my "I'm sure."


translate English day7_ef4defcf:


    my "I love it... {w}I lied about hating it."


translate English day7_2e25ccae:


    nar "She cocks her head to one side while gazing out the window. {w}I wonder what she's thinking about?"


translate English day7_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_fd18bcae:


    my "I had no idea a place like this even existed in the capital..."


translate English day7_6b401433:


    my "I've always thought of the capital as this magical place filled with sparkling lights, so different from where I used to live... That it was so beautiful."


translate English day7_83c456fd:


    pl "You never really visited the capital before?"


translate English day7_92a835eb:


    my "I'd come with friends on occasion..."


translate English day7_093af7bf:


    pl "Friends, huh?"


translate English day7_97dca47d:


    nar "As I look into her eyes that are full of memories of her past, there's no denying the impure emotions that are suddenly growing inside me."


translate English day7_ae5c4d76:


    nar "She has other friends that she spends time with."


translate English day7_9a3a7ccd:


    nar "I don't really know anything about Maya. {w}As I sit here worrying about her, she's thinking about people from her past life that I've never met."


translate English day7_d17b99ab:


    nar "It seems pretty obvious, and yet for some reason, I'd been in denial about it."


translate English day7_d7126600:


    nar "Is it okay to want to keep someone all to yourself simply because you feel a certain way about them?"


translate English day7_0085ba34:


    my "Just because I had fun in the past doesn't mean I didn't have fun today. {w}I enjoyed it a lot."


translate English day7_6ac0c62b:


    pl "Really? {w}I'm glad! I had a lot of fun today, too. {w}I mean, getting a break from that suffocating place is nice."


translate English day7_53bcd9b0:


    my "Yeah. I'm glad you feel the same way. {w}Though I feel bad that I ruined everyone's good time..."


translate English day7_4a835f11:


    nar "She still looks gloomy. {w}I can tell that she's already trying to forget everything that happened today."


translate English day7_5087a37a:


    nar "Maya doesn't feel guilty about it. {w}And of course, she doesn't blame the children for what happened."


translate English day7_b6f3ac72:


    nar "No one did anything wrong... {w}The fact that no one was to blame for what happened is an optimistic outlook while also being surprisingly cruel."


translate English day7_9efe9c9c:


    pl "I'm sorry about earlier... {w}I should have been protecting you."


translate English day7_3ecdf669:


    my "It's not like I asked you to. It's fine. Plus, I don't want you to feel responsible..."


translate English day7_7ce9d0b3:


    pl "Was it just that you were surprised?"


translate English day7_d07efd34:


    my "I wasn't surprised and I'm not angry..."


translate English day7_b85f9f29:


    my "It seems like lately... Mm, sometimes, I have these weird visions..."


translate English day7_11d916a7:


    pl "Weird? Like how?"


translate English day7_aae5bd16:


    my "They're very scary... Horrifying even..."


translate English day7_1392f6c7:


    nar "I'm instantly reminded of my dreams. {w}My nightmares that have been plaguing me for days now, becoming almost like a sickening routine of sorts."


translate English day7_eabbcac5:


